      <description>Hi, thanks for the fast reply... &#13;
&#13;
I'm using revision 5 and i mean the text of the email...&#13;
&#13;
After reading the thread you sugested... I've changed this line of the hack:&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
$mail-&gt;setContentType( "multipart/mixed;boundary=$mime_boundary",false,false,false);&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
for this:&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
$mail-&gt;setContentType( "multipart/mixed",false,false,false,$mime_boundary);&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
... and now the encoding is right. :)&#13;
&#13;
Thanks a lot!</description>
