      <description>The package of the Enhanced eZBinaryFile extension available for download within this project's downloads is the latest version compatible with eZ Publish 4.x &lt;= 4.6 (Tested with eZ Publish 4.5)&#13;
&#13;
If you wish to use the Enhanced eZBinaryFile extension for eZ Publish 3.x through 3.10.x then please download the older version which is eZ Publish 3.x+ compatible directly from the older version's project website. &#13;
&#13;
Remember this extension has a separate project for the eZ Publish 3.x+ version through it the eZ Publish 3.x+ compatible version is available, http://projects.ez.no/enhancedezbinaryfile&#13;
&#13;
If you wish to use the Enhanced eZBinaryFile extension for eZ Publish 4.x+ then please download the latest version from this project's downloads or subversion repository!&#13;
http://projects.ez.no/enhancedezbinaryfile/downloads&#13;
&#13;
Worth noting is that the project for the eZ Publish 3.x version is clearly not maintained any longer (also it is a project imported from the older ez.no contributions section, and these seem to have remained unmaintained since long before the migration).&#13;
&#13;
I hope this helps other users looking to obtain the features this extension provides in a very simple to use all in one solution.&#13;
