      <title>some changes</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/enhancedezbinaryfile/forum/general/some_changes</link>
      <description>Hi,&#13;
&#13;
i did some changes to your extension.&#13;
&#13;
- i add the functionallity that uploaded files are removed if the collection is removed in admin&#13;
=&gt; requires a 2. patch&#13;
For that i change the storage dir format&#13;
&#13;
old:  storage/original/attachments/image/...&#13;
new:  storage/original/attachments/ $ContentObjectID / $CollectionID / image/...&#13;
&#13;
The new format enables us easily to remove a single collection or all collections for an object.&#13;
&#13;
- i did some code refactoring  (coding style, unix line endings ...)&#13;
&#13;
- enabling filecheck operator (i got an warning in admin interface)&#13;
&#13;
I can send you my changes or i can commit to svn if you want.&#13;
&#13;
Now it is working :-) on our ez440 installations.&#13;
&#13;
Thank's for sharing this extension.</description>
