      <description>I am using SMTP mail transport, rather than sendmail to email uploaded files and am finding the mail that sends contains an incorrect content-type header.  It is coming across as 'text/mixed' rather than 'multipart/mixed'.  I suspect this has coming to do with ezMail-&gt;setContentType() only setting the subType of content type.&#13;
