      <description>Hi Hachem,&#13;
&#13;
Try to change this code in "kernel/content/collectinformation.php":&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
if (file_exists( eZSys::wwwDir()."/".$Filename )) {&#13;
        $fileAttachments[]=array(eZSys::wwwDir()."/".$Filename, $OriginalFilename, $FileType);&#13;
}&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
for this:&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
if (file_exists( $Filename )) {&#13;
        $fileAttachments[]=array($Filename, $OriginalFilename, $FileType);&#13;
}&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
Regards.&#13;
</description>
